OL,3,C'No reason' to delay enthronement over
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak, new Archbishop
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe Archbishop of Canterbury told ITV
OL,8,FMeridian that current advice from the
OL,9,FUK Health Security Agency states there
OL,10,Fis 'no reason' for the diocese to
OL,11,Fpostpone her enthronement ceremony
OL,13,FDame Sarah Mullally has insisted her
OL,14,Fenthronement as the next Archbishop of
OL,15,FCanterbury will still go ahead as
OL,16,Fplanned despite the outbreak of
OL,17,Fmeningitis in the city.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
