PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773997500
OL,3,C'No reason' to delay enthronement over
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak, new Archbishop
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FTwo students have died in the
OL,8,Foutbreak, while 27 cases, as of
OL,9,FWednesday morning, have been confirmed
OL,10,Fby the UK Health Security Agency
OL,11,F(UKHSA).
OL,13,FDame Sarah told ITV Meridian that the
OL,14,Fdiocese is in contact with the agency,
OL,15,Fexplaining "their advice at the moment
OL,16,Fis there is no reason why it should
OL,17,Fnot go ahead".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
