PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773997500
OL,3,C'No reason' to delay enthronement over
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak, new Archbishop
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FShe is due to be enthroned as the
OL,8,FArchbishop of Canterbury at the city's
OL,9,Fcathedral next Wednesday (March 25) -
OL,10,Fwhen she will become the first female
OL,11,Fto officially hold the role in the
OL,12,FChurch of England's near 500-year
OL,13,Fhistory.
OL,15,FThe former bishop of London made the
OL,16,Fcomments on Wednesday as she began the
OL,17,Fthird day of her 87-mile pilgrimage
OL,18,Ffrom St Paul's Cathedral to Canterbury
OL,19,FCathedral.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773997500
OL,3,C'No reason' to delay enthronement over
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak, new Archbishop
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FShe is the first Archbishop of
OL,8,FCanterbury in modern history to
OL,9,Fundertake the journey ahead of her
OL,10,Fenthronement, and will complete it on
OL,11,FSunday.
OL,13,FDame Sarah said: "We're in contact
OL,14,Fwith the UKHSA and their advice at the
OL,15,Fmoment is there is no reason why it
OL,16,F(enthronement) should not go ahead.
OL,26,@xD@ApmxD@Npn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
