PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773997500
OL,3,C'No reason' to delay enthronement over
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak, new Archbishop
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"We have written to people to reassure
OL,8,Fthem about that, but also to reassure
OL,9,Fthem that we continue to be in
OL,10,Fconversation with them and will take
OL,11,Ftheir advice."
OL,13,FThe Archbishop of Canterbury began
OL,14,FWednesday's leg of her pilgrimage
OL,15,Fsetting off from the town of Strood.
OL,17,FDame Sarah told ITV Meridian 'it's
OL,18,Fbeen a joy to meet people' on her
OL,19,Fpilgrimage to Canterbury Cathedral
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
