PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773997500
OL,3,C'No reason' to delay enthronement over
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak, new Archbishop
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FShe was accompanied by the local
OL,8,Fclergy of Rochester and, en-route, met
OL,9,Fwith a group of community gardeners.
OL,11,FDame Sarah said that it had been
OL,12,F"lovely" to meet people on her
OL,13,Fjourney, adding: "The fact that you
OL,14,Fwalk slowly you see so many things
OL,15,Fyou've never seen.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
