PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773997500
OL,3,C'No reason' to delay enthronement over
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak, new Archbishop
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"The contrast and the landscape and
OL,8,Findustry, but also it's been a joy to
OL,9,Fmeet people - whether they're on their
OL,10,Fdog walk or whether, for example this
OL,11,Fmorning at St Barnabas (church), in a
OL,12,Ftime of prayer."
OL,14,FThe Prince of Wales will represent the
OL,15,FKing - who acts as supreme governor of
OL,16,Fthe Church of England - at the
OL,17,Fenthronement ceremony. He will be
OL,18,Fjoined by the Princess of Wales.
OL,26,@sD@XpmsD@_pn
